            <title>
                <![CDATA[華爾街日報惹議，數據機構 Elliptic 澄清：嚴重誇大哈馬斯加密捐款]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">分析機構 Elliptic 的數據被引用在華爾街日報的爭議文章中，Elliptic 對此出面澄清，稱該報導錯誤引用了數據，但即便如此，該文記者仍拒絕撤回報導，並在推特上捍衞立場。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_57 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-653b164f8371c"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-653b164f8371c"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%EF%BC%9F" title="華爾街日報是否誇大事實？">華爾街日報是否誇大事實？</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4" title="Elliptic：華爾街日報有誤">Elliptic：華爾街日報有誤</a></li><li class="insert-page-1 insert-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/elliptic-counters-wsj-report/#Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%80%85%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6" title="Elliptic：正與相關者合作釐清事實">Elliptic：正與相關者合作釐清事實</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%87%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%EF%BC%9F"></span><strong>華爾街日報是否誇大事實？</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>之前華爾街日報曾報導「哈馬斯相關加密錢包收到了 4,100 萬美元」，這不僅讓大眾再次加深對加密貨幣的負面觀感，同時也加重潛在監管壓力，被反加密出名的參議員 Elizabeth Warren 用來趁勢推動《數位資產反洗錢法案》。</p><p><strong>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/hamas-linked-crypto-accounts-frozen-by-israeli-police-with-help-of-binance" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以巴衝突持續，幣安與以色列合作扣押哈馬斯帳户，以斷其金援</a>)</strong></p><p>Messari 創辦人兼執行長 Ryan Selkis 就曾表示，哈馬斯早發現加密貨幣具有可追溯性，並在四月份就已停止使用加密貨幣進行募款。</p><p><a href="https://www.elliptic.co/blog/setting-the-record-straight-on-crypto-crowdfunding-by-hamas" target="_blank" rel="noopener">加密分析機構 Elliptic</a> 在 10 月 25 日更以長文反駁華爾街日報。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%9C%89%E8%AA%A4"></span><strong>Elliptic：華爾街日報有誤</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>華爾街日報在報導中引用了 Elliptic 的數據，稱從 2021 年 8 月到今年 6 月，與聖戰組織 (PIJ) 關聯的錢包收到了高達 9,300 萬美元的加密貨幣。</p><p>報導也引用另一機構 BitOK 的數據，稱哈馬斯相關錢包在同時期收到約 4,100 萬美元。</p><p>Elliptic 對此澄清幾點：</p><ol><li><p>10 月 7 日至今，哈馬斯僅收到 21,000 美元加密貨幣，且火速遭凍結。</p></li><li><p>PIJ 錢包是「收到」了 9,300 萬美元加密貨幣，絕對不代表他們募到這麼多錢。</p></li><li><p>這些錢包也涉及交易所錢包，並無法確定資金是否皆屬 PIJ 所有。</p></li></ol><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Elliptic%EF%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%80%85%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6"></span><strong>Elliptic：正與相關者合作釐清事實</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Elliptic 表示正與參議員 Elizabeth Warren 的代表、華爾街日報作者交涉，以澄清事實。</p><p>不過該篇文章的記者 Ian Talley 似乎非常堅持最初的報導，即便眾多加密社羣向他呼籲立即撤回報導，他仍持續在推文中引用能支持他論點的數據。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">"Digital-currency wallets that Israeli authorities linked to the PIJ received as much as $93 million in crypto between August 2021 and June this year, analysis by leading crypto researcher Elliptic showed."</p><p>"It couldn’t be determined whether the crypto they received was directly…</p><p>— Ian Talley (@IanTalley) <a href="https://twitter.com/IanTalley/status/1717300164635906282?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 25, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
